To install extra modelus used in this solution run:
pip install -r requirements.txt 

Following program contains two scripts the first one is microservice.py.
Run this script with: 

python3 microservice.py

To test this solution you can run second script with

python3 test.py

Test script contains two requests with post method, one put method that edits movie title from first post.
Last two requests test GET method for one movie with id 1 and request to get all movies.

----------------Docker
To pull the docker:
docker pull nakamize/micro-python-flask
Run docker with:
docker container run -d -p 8000:8000 nakamize/micro-python-flask:latest